Getting a YES to milk🙄 that's a tough one.

My children just don't like the taste of milk, but I always say NO to almost all milk mixes. They may be tasty, but they're just filled with maida and refined sugar! That's where the Magic Milk Mix from @slurrpfarm gets it right. Slurrp Farm understands that mothers need an option that makes milk MORE healthy for our children, not less! Magic Milk Mix replaces maida with jowar and oats, refined sugar with only jaggery - so it's just so easy to say YES! #YesKaTimeAaGaya

No other place in the world is as safe as a Mom’s embrace. 
Protecting our little ones from the monsters under the bed 🛌 or dressing them up as their favorite Superhero 🦸‍♀️ We Mamas have always got their back.  The look of concern, those extra precautions that we take, and the superpowers that make us a bodyguard, a soothing advisor, and the wall that stands between kids and trouble all the time, is what makes us their best savior. 🤗 This Mother’s Day, let’s celebrate ourselves and a mother’s love and care, and the fact that #MamaKeepsYouSafe, always!
